{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"rl01","text":"Several years ago, I went to a Queens of the Stone Age show. I saw a similar lighting effect done with LEDs hanging from the ceiling, and it has always stuck with me. I wanted to see if I could recreate the effect in a basic web experience.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}
